f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661ea3596ab2369062819470bd2a42fc97e2cbdf","tid":2158440,"uid":112502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ffe2a9ff03d844a85f9f9a277bd1a4958bc1079f","tid":2158440,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:39:01.000Z","msg":"即係話收你dna可以知道你個樣<br />\n但政府本身已經知道晒你個樣同資料，係你身份證影過，實準過用dna推<br />\n仲有d咩有用資料？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">疑犯塔爾博特一直潛逃，執法機關的通緝名單上從未出現他的名字，警方一度苦無線索。但警方繼上月以新的基因族譜技術，拘捕潛逃多年的金州殺手迪安杰洛（Joseph James DeAngelo）後，再次以此技術追捕懸案兇手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方利用在情侶的小型貨車中收集到的疑犯DNA樣本，按其DNA特徵模擬出疑犯的拼圖，然後將他的基因型（genotype）與基因族譜（genetic-genealogy）網站資料對比，先找出塔爾博特的兩名親屬，然後再鎖定他。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20180521/Y5J6RNP3UXIWXDGW476BBJ4XPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180521%2FY5J6RNP3UXIWXDGW476BBJ4XPY%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=64fa5b71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180521%2FY5J6RNP3UXIWXDGW476BBJ4XPY%2F&h=59cca66a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20180521/Y5J6RNP3UXIWXDGW476BBJ4XPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有類似技術，只要香港個基因庫夠大，一定唔少勇武比人抽後算賬，上年如果有popo執gas mask都應該搵到好多DNA，衝立法會事後都有人搜DNA"},{"pid":"f5398970f7816447f2ce3264397226b5547539b1","tid":2158440,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffe2a9ff03d844a85f9f9a277bd1a4958bc1079f","tid":2158440,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:39:01.000Z","msg":"即係話收你dna可以知道你個樣<br />\n但政府本身已經知道晒你個樣同資料，係你身份證影過，實準過用dna推<br />\n仲有d咩有用資料？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"呢一樣野就要講埋所謂嘅鑑證（唔太熟 有錯請指證）<br />\n上年七一入立會後第二日 班狗去哂現場搜指紋等等<br />\n<br />\n如果當時嘅搜證到呢加仲留底咗 十年後技術成熟後一樣可以照search 哂出黎<br />\n<br />\n以往好多咩古今奇案之類近十年都破哂案<br />\n當然有啲追溯唔到<br />\n<br />\n但呢一個係個好嚴重私隱問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347ba6c582a5e08ba42923af45beda0b19222c02","tid":2158440,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4fadca313053c7c30f94e5e1b8df27818c9752a","tid":2158440,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e674a55240046ea9e066c3997d81b5c462d7fe","tid":2158440,"uid":196329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3794d24d875434541421e39a463814510f28910e","tid":2158440,"uid":268547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ffe2a9ff03d844a85f9f9a277bd1a4958bc1079f","tid":2158440,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:39:01.000Z","msg":"即係話收你dna可以知道你個樣<br />\n但政府本身已經知道晒你個樣同資料，係你身份證影過，實準過用dna推<br />\n仲有d咩有用資料？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:04:51.000Z","msg":"你唔聽話,係咪可以 捏造一個有你dna精液嘅報告?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"你唔聽話直接國安拉你都得啦<br />\n夾硬黎講，仲有要造假拉你返差館搵包粉將你指模hi上去咪得，攞黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"唔聽話直接搞鳩你係無錯，DNA應該係針對一d做過唔聽話既野，又成功隱藏身份既人，唔小心留低DNA就幾年後出國果陣無啦啦係機埸截住都唔出奇"},{"pid":"0d89c4358bc9eb64915a8b828ec7c40f4ba4badb","tid":2158440,"uid":84408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"最重要嘅係身份證有假<br />\n樣可以整容<br />\n但DNA無得變<br />\n而且仲好容易驗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2120a8e19a9c7196a971a78dab07c9bb2c77c0ee","tid":2158440,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ff1ebd89cf59b44735b1d10da2c22a42f3ccd1","tid":2158